Pick the perfect pizza restaurant 
Decide if you want take out or delivery as options may vary based on what you choose
View the menu and decide on what you want to eat 
Place your order 
With a delivery order, sit patiently as your food will arrive shortly. With a takeout order, you should be now making your way to pick it up
Devour food 
Clean up pizza boxes as well as any other item that you have ordered
Let your food digest 